metadata.symbol: Art for the next century, whenever it arrives
metadata.description:
The visualization of an electro-acoustic sound piece consisting of animal, insect, and alternative nature sounds along with electronic associations: Upon encountering a scene with an aural theme redolent of quasi-natural sounds from animals that might have never lived and robotic voicings that seem part of the landscape instead of the speaking of its populace, a denouement of silence occurs when sound becomes a sight revealing that the ambience is ultimately human.

(The unlockable content is the 1920 x 1080 MP4, 04 minutes 09 seconds.)
metadata.title: Dear Idea
metadata.subtitle: Ideas Are The Dearest Things
